      • DELETED

        static final java.lang.String DELETED

        Key indicating a deletion.

        This value can appear as the value of a key in a configuration or as a key itself. If used as a key, the whole configuration is flagged as deleted from its parent when computing the overlay.

        See Also:

      • LIB_PREFIX

        static final java.lang.String LIB_PREFIX
        The prefix for attributes that specify additional libraries to add to ${karaf.home}/lib. These are native libraries only. JARs that should be available in app classpath should go to ${karaf.home}/lib/boot and use BOOT_PREFIX.
        See Also:
